          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-slate-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <a href="/multi-document" class="ml-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-700 transition-colors">
                Multi-Document Workflows
              </a>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <svg class="flex-shrink-0 h-5 w-5 text-slate-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M7.293 14.707a1 1 0 010-1.414L10.586 10 7.293 6.707a1 1 0 011.414-1.414l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
              </svg>
              <span class="ml-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-900">
                Document Fusion
              </span>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-slate-50 to-blue-100 py-16">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 text-blue-600 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
          <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="7 16V4m0 0L3 8m4-4l4 4m6 0v12m0 0l4-4m-4 4l-4-4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">
          Document Fusion
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Watch AI combine multiple distinct inputs to create unified, comprehensive outputs that 
          no single document could provide. This is synthesis at its finest.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pattern Overview -->
  <section class="py-12 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-2">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6">How Fusion Works</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-700">
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Document fusion goes beyond simple combination‚Äîit creates <em>new value</em> by finding 
              connections, patterns, and complementary information across disparate sources. The AI acts 
              as an intelligent synthesizer, understanding context and creating coherent narratives.
            </p>
            <p class="leading-relaxed">
              Unlike basic concatenation, fusion involves cross-referencing, validation, and strategic 
              organization. The AI identifies which elements from each document support or enhance others, 
              creating a result that's more valuable than the sum of its parts.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-blue-100">
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-blue-900 mb-4">The Fusion Process</h3>
            <div class="space-y-3">
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-200 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mr-3 mt-0.5">1</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-900">Individual Analysis</h4>
                  <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">Each document analyzed for key themes, data points, and unique contributions</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-200 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mr-3 mt-0.5">2</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-900">Cross-Reference Mapping</h4>
                  <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">AI identifies relationships, contradictions, and complementary information</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-200 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mr-3 mt-0.5">3</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-900">Strategic Synthesis</h4>
                  <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">Information combined with hierarchical structure and narrative flow</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start">
                <div class="w-6 h-6 bg-blue-200 text-blue-800 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold mr-3 mt-0.5">4</div>
                <div>
                  <h4 class="font-medium text-blue-900">Quality Validation</h4>
                  <p class="text-blue-700 text-sm">Cross-checking facts and ensuring consistency across the fused document</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Common Fusion Scenarios</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Academic tenure portfolios from CV + evaluations + letters</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Product evaluations from vendor specs + user feedback + technical reviews</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Grant proposals from research plans + budget + institutional support</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Investment reports from financial data + market analysis + risk assessments</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2 mr-3 flex-shrink-0"></div>
              <span>Compliance documents from policies + audit results + remediation plans</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Conversation Example -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4">Academic Tenure Packet Fusion</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          See how AI combines a CV, teaching evaluations, and peer review letters into a comprehensive tenure evaluation
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <ChatConversation 
        messages={tenurePacketConversation}
        title="Multi-Document Academic Portfolio Creation"
        description="Academic committee creating comprehensive tenure evaluation from multiple sources"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Deep Dive Analysis -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 text-center">The Magic of Fusion</h2>
      
      <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <!-- Left: What Happened -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">What Just Happened?</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-blue-400 pl-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Multi-Source Intelligence</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
                The AI didn't just read three documents‚Äîit <em>understood their relationships</em>. 
                It validated peer review claims against CV achievements and connected teaching excellence 
                to research impact.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-green-400 pl-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Cross-Validation Process</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
                Notice how the AI cited specific papers from the CV when peer reviewers mentioned them, 
                and quantified teaching success with actual evaluation scores. This creates credible, 
                evidence-based narratives.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-4 border-purple-400 pl-6">
              <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-2">Strategic Synthesis</h4>
              <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">
                The final executive summary wasn't just a list‚Äîit was strategically organized to match 
                tenure committee needs, with quantified achievements and clear recommendations.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Right: The Value -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-6">Why This Creates Value</h3>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-200 mb-6">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">Before AI Fusion:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Hours of manual cross-referencing</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Risk of missing key connections</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Inconsistent evaluation criteria</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-red-400 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Subjective narrative construction</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-green-200">
            <h4 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-4">With AI Fusion:</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Automatic cross-document validation</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Comprehensive pattern recognition</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Consistent evaluation framework</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center">
                <div class="w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-green-500 rounded-full mr-3"></div>
                <span>Evidence-based narrative construction</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Insights -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-slate-900">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-6">The Fusion Advantage</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed mb-8">
        <span class="text-blue-400 font-semibold">Fusion creates exponential value.</span>
        When AI combines documents intelligently, it doesn't just save time‚Äîit discovers insights 
        that humans would miss and creates more comprehensive, reliable outputs.
      </p>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">1+1+1</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400 mb-2">=</div>
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">7</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-sm">Multiplicative Value Creation</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">90%</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Time Reduction</div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-2">0</div>
          <div class="text-slate-400">Missed Connections</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>